Title: The Geometry of Electric Charge: The Charge Characteristic Class
Authors: G.H.Gadiyar
Comments: (Latex file 6 pages) e-mail: padma@imsc.ernet.in -IITM-TH-94-02
\\
  It is well known that magnetic monopoles are related to the first Chern
class. In this note electric charge is used to construct an analogous
characteristic class: the charge class.
